<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>S2R BUILD | Impactis Consulting</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --navy:#1B3F7A;--navy-dk:#0F2550;--red:#8C1A1A;
  --bg:#F8F7F4;--surf:#FFFFFF;--surf2:#F2F0EC;
  --bdr:#E2DFD8;--bdr2:#CCC9C0;
  --tx:#1A1A2E;--tx2:#4A4A5E;--tx3:#8A8A9E;
  --build-bg:#F0EBF8;--build-bd:#9B8FD8;--build-tx:#3C2A8C;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--tx);min-height:100vh}

.topnav{background:var(--navy-dk);padding:0 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:58px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--build-bd)}
.nav-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.9rem}
.back-btn{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.73rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border-radius:6px;padding:.3rem .7rem;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s}
.back-btn:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);color:#fff}
.nav-title{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75)}
.build-pip{background:var(--build-bd);color:#fff;font-size:.66rem;font-weight:700;padding:.22rem .6rem;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.06em}

.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy-dk) 0%,#1C2E6B 55%,#2A1A5A 100%);padding:2.5rem 1.5rem 2.25rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 12% 65%,rgba(155,143,216,.18) 0%,transparent 48%),radial-gradient(circle at 88% 18%,rgba(45,100,200,.12) 0%,transparent 42%)}
.hero-inner{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;position:relative}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--build-bd);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.hero-h1{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:2rem;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:.55rem;font-weight:400}
.hero-h1 em{color:#C4B4F8;font-style:normal}
.hero-p{font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);max-width:600px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
.hero-stats{display:flex;gap:.65rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hstat{background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);padding:.28rem .82rem;border-radius:20px;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:500}

.main{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;padding:1.75rem 1.5rem 5rem}

.progress-bar-wrap{background:var(--surf);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:10px;padding:.85rem 1.1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.pb-label{font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--tx);white-space:nowrap}
.pb-track{flex:1;min-width:120px;height:7px;background:var(--bdr2);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.pb-fill{height:100%;background:var(--build-bd);border-radius:4px;width:9%}
.pb-stat{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--tx3);white-space:nowrap}

.camp-block{margin-bottom:2.5rem}
.camp-hdr{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.85rem;margin-bottom:1rem;padding-bottom:.65rem;border-bottom:2px solid var(--bdr)}
.camp-num{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0}
.c1 .camp-num{background:var(--build-bg);color:var(--build-tx);border:2px solid var(--build-bd)}
.c2 .camp-num{background:#E8F0FF;color:#1A3A8A;border:2px solid #5A80D0}
.c3 .camp-num{background:#E8F8F0;color:#0A4A2A;border:2px solid #2AB07A}
.camp-name{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--tx)}
.camp-meta{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--tx3);margin-top:2px}
.camp-tag{font-size:.64rem;font-weight:700;padding:.18rem .5rem;border-radius:10px;margin-left:.5rem;vertical-align:middle}
.c1 .camp-tag{background:var(--build-bg);color:var(--build-tx);border:1px solid var(--build-bd)}
.c2 .camp-tag{background:#E8F0FF;color:#1A3A8A;border:1px solid #5A80D0}
.c3 .camp-tag{background:#E8F8F0;color:#0A4A2A;border:1px solid #2AB07A}

.lens-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:.75rem}
.lens-card{background:var(--surf);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:12px;padding:1rem 1.1rem;transition:all .2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-top:3px solid var(--bdr2);text-decoration:none;display:block}
.lens-card.active{border-top-color:var(--build-bd);cursor:pointer}
.lens-card.active:hover{border-color:var(--build-bd);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 5px 18px rgba(60,42,140,.12)}
.lens-card.coming{opacity:.5;cursor:default}
.lc-num{font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.3rem}
.lens-card.active .lc-num{color:var(--build-bd)}
.lc-title{font-size:.88rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--tx);margin-bottom:.28rem;line-height:1.3}
.lc-desc{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:.65rem}
.lc-arcs{display:flex;gap:3px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:.55rem}
.lc-arc{font-size:.6rem;font-weight:600;padding:.15rem .4rem;border-radius:8px;background:var(--surf2);color:var(--tx3);border:1px solid var(--bdr)}
.lens-card.active .lc-arc{background:var(--build-bg);color:var(--build-tx);border-color:var(--build-bd)}
.lc-action{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--build-tx)}
.lc-coming{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--tx3);font-style:italic}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="topnav">
  <div class="nav-left">
    <a class="back-btn" href="index.html">← S2R Home</a>
    <span class="nav-title">BUILD Module</span>
  </div>
  <span class="build-pip">3 CAMPS · 11 LENSES</span>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Strategy2Results® · BUILD</div>
    <h1 class="hero-h1"><em>Build</em> your strategy.<br>Lens by lens.</h1>
    <p class="hero-p">Three Base Camps. Eleven structured lenses. Each lens builds on the last — from aligning your leadership team through to grounding your strategy for durable execution.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <span class="hstat">⛺ 3 Base Camps</span>
      <span class="hstat">🔭 11 Lenses</span>
      <span class="hstat">⏱ 2 full days</span>
      <span class="hstat">👥 Full CXO team required</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main">

  <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
    <span class="pb-label">Your BUILD progress</span>
    <div class="pb-track"><div class="pb-fill"></div></div>
    <span class="pb-stat">1 of 11 lenses active</span>
  </div>

  <!-- CAMP 1 -->
  <div class="camp-block c1">
    <div class="camp-hdr">
      <div class="camp-num">1</div>
      <div>
        <div class="camp-name">Base Camp 1: Direction <span class="camp-tag">Day 1 · 4 lenses</span></div>
        <div class="camp-meta">Where are we going — and why does it matter?</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lens-grid">
      <a class="lens-card active" href="lens_01_heartmind.html">
        <div class="lc-num">Lens 01</div>
        <div class="lc-title">Aligning Heart & Mind</div>
        <div class="lc-desc">Team behavioural DNA, climate diagnostic, and alignment architecture.</div>
        <div class="lc-arcs">
          <span class="lc-arc">Awareness</span>
          <span class="lc-arc">Intelligence</span>
          <span class="lc-arc">Extrapolating</span>
          <span class="lc-arc">Converging</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lc-action">Enter lens →</div>
      </a>
      <div class="lens-card coming">
        <div class="lc-num">Lens 02</div>
        <div class="lc-title">Strategy Visioning & SiP</div>
        <div class="lc-desc">Strategic intent, Success in Practice picture, and direction definition.</div>
        <div class="lc-arcs"><span class="lc-arc">Awareness</span><span class="lc-arc">Intelligence</span><span class="lc-arc">Extrapolating</span><span class="lc-arc">Converging</span></div>
        <div class="lc-coming">Building next</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lens-card coming">
        <div class="lc-num">Lens 03</div>
        <div class="lc-title">KISS Mapping & OKR Design</div>
        <div class="lc-desc">Strategic priorities, trade-offs, and OKR architecture.</div>
        <div class="lc-arcs"><span class="lc-arc">Awareness</span><span class="lc-arc">Intelligence</span><span class="lc-arc">Extrapolating</span><span class="lc-arc">Converging</span></div>
        <div class="lc-coming">Coming</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lens-card coming">
        <div class="lc-num">Lens 04</div>
        <div class="lc-title">ABCV Integrity Check</div>
        <div class="lc-desc">Ambition, Boldness, Coherence, and Value alignment audit.</div>
        <div class="lc-arcs"><span class="lc-arc">Awareness</span><span class="lc-arc">Intelligence</span><span class="lc-arc">Extrapolating</span><span class="lc-arc">Converging</span></div>
        <div class="lc-coming">Coming</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CAMP 2 -->
  <div class="camp-block c2">
    <div class="camp-hdr">
      <div class="camp-num">2</div>
      <div>
        <div class="camp-name">Base Camp 2: Influence <span class="camp-tag">Day 1 · 4 lenses</span></div>
        <div class="camp-meta">How do we deliver — and who owns what?</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lens-grid">
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 05</div><div class="lc-title">Stakeholder Mapping</div><div class="lc-desc">Power, influence, and engagement architecture.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 06</div><div class="lc-title">Narrative & 4W Design</div><div class="lc-desc">Strategic narrative construction across all stakeholder layers.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 07</div><div class="lc-title">Influence Architecture</div><div class="lc-desc">CXO expectations register and accountability design.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 08</div><div class="lc-title">Change Levers</div><div class="lc-desc">Activation levers and performance management rhythm.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CAMP 3 -->
  <div class="camp-block c3">
    <div class="camp-hdr">
      <div class="camp-num">3</div>
      <div>
        <div class="camp-name">Base Camp 3: Grounding <span class="camp-tag">Day 2 · 3 lenses</span></div>
        <div class="camp-meta">What makes this durable — and what threatens it?</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lens-grid">
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 09</div><div class="lc-title">Risk & Stress Testing</div><div class="lc-desc">Where the strategy breaks under pressure.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 10</div><div class="lc-title">Communication Design</div><div class="lc-desc">Cascade architecture and white space mapping.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
      <div class="lens-card coming"><div class="lc-num">Lens 11</div><div class="lc-title">Grounding Plan</div><div class="lc-desc">Culture, ESRG, and FIT operating rhythm.</div><div class="lc-coming">Coming</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
